==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inseparably
<hw>In*sep"a*ra*bly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an inseparable manner
or condition; so as not to be separable.</def>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And cleaves through life <qex>inseparably</qex> close.</q>
<rj><qau>Cowper.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inseparate</ent>⟦br⟧
